{"tid":1134691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又贏] 涉向華洩露美國機密資料 港產前中情局人員改認罪","createTime":"2019-05-01T23:57:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T14:25:03.000Z","uid":141151,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fe3467bf36d9f44549dcef40e6a7d89417f417fe","tid":1134691,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T23:57:54.000Z","msg":"涉向華洩露美國機密資料 港產前中情局人員改認罪<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.singtao.ca/3416775/2019-05-01/news-%e6%b6%89%e5%90%91%e8%8f%af%e6%b4%a9%e9%9c%b2%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e6%a9%9f%e5%af%86%e8%b3%87%e6%96%99++%e6%b8%af%e7%94%a2%e5%89%8d%e4%b8%ad%e6%83%85%e5%b1%80%e4%ba%ba%e5%93%a1%e6%94%b9%e8%aa%8d%e7%bd%aa/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.singtao.ca%2F3416775%2F2019-05-01%2Fnews-%25e6%25b6%2589%25e5%2590%2591%25e8%258f%25af%25e6%25b4%25a9%25e9%259c%25b2%25e7%25be%258e%25e5%259c%258b%25e6%25a9%259f%25e5%25af%2586%25e8%25b3%2587%25e6%2596%2599%2B%2B%25e6%25b8%25af%25e7%2594%25a2%25e5%2589%258d%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e6%2583%2585%25e5%25b1%2580%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e5%2593%25a1%25e6%2594%25b9%25e8%25aa%258d%25e7%25bd%25aa%2F&d=P2v3VPQ3iBAPr6cjv61qmRPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=61506435\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.singtao.ca/3416775/2019-05-01/news-%e6%b6%89%e5%90%91%e8%8f%af%e6%b4%a9%e9%9c%b2%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e6%a9%9f%e5%af%86%e8%b3%87%e6%96%99++%e6%b8%af%e7%94%a2%e5%89%8d%e4%b8%ad%e6%83%85%e5%b1%80%e4%ba%ba%e5%93%a1%e6%94%b9%e8%aa%8d%e7%bd%aa/</a><br />\n<br />\n擁有香港永久居留權的前美國中情局（CIA）情報人員李振成（Jerry Chun Shing Lee），去年1月被美國指控為中國當間諜後一直還押，同年5月被控三項間諜罪名，指李振成向中國政府透露危害美國的國防資料，最高可被判終身監禁。李振成早前於預審中不認罪，但根據美國法庭文件紀錄，顯示李振成會於當地時間周三（1日）認罪。<br />\n<br />\n根據法庭文件紀錄，李振成將於周三在維珍尼亞州亞歷山德里亞聯邦法院，出席更改答辯聆訊（change-of-plea hearing）。法庭文件紀錄沒有顯示他將會承認哪一條控罪，亦不清楚他是否會請求較輕的指控或較輕的判決，而李的代表律師回覆媒體時，表示不予置評。<br />\n<br />\n起訴書披露，李振成由2010年起接觸中國情報官員，對方更即時給他10萬美元現金及提出「照顧他一生」（they would take care of him for life）來換取合作，中間人是曾任香港警察、李的生意拍檔。約兩周後，李振成主動向一名CIA前同事匯報，曾有中方人員接觸，但並無提及金錢回報及照顧他一生之說。<br />\n<br />\n直到2012年初，有美國情報人員在中國被殺害和拘禁，美國傳媒指他重創美國在華諜網，並可能導致美國至少20名CIA特工在俄羅斯被曝光、捉拿及殺害。CIA開始對李振成起疑，通知聯邦調查局（FBI），FBI探員在李於2012年返美期間，在其下榻酒店房間發現懷疑私通中國的證據，包括兩本寫有中情局人員和卧底的真實姓名、電話號碼等資料的記事簿。李振成於去年1月在紐約的甘迺迪國際機場被捕。"},{"pid":"b23d9a18b1d157a28fa3aead1bc17e448eac58d2","tid":1134691,"uid":196552,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T00:05:26.000Z","msg":"等美國黎照顧佢一生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e591f5543fd0dccbc0bc5b133af9185b01950341","tid":1134691,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T00:19:25.000Z","msg":"關係法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a23b86525145376ef99fec6b8b6db3e7e5932f12","tid":1134691,"uid":156511,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"b23d9a18b1d157a28fa3aead1bc17e448eac58d2","tid":1134691,"uid":196552,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T00:05:26.000Z","msg":"等美國黎照顧佢一生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T00:26:12.000Z","msg":"中國政府有口恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講得出做得到<br />\n真。Take care for life"},{"pid":"e2811d440980af83ea79ec826f9162aa568c847d","tid":1134691,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:48:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4f5d62e9638d83f6499dee0b653f839298ed67","tid":1134691,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T02:01:40.000Z","msg":"堅係害死人嘅case"},{"pid":"250450873bcb6e58afbee27f1e6b946520a3c435","tid":1134691,"uid":117679,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T02:04:06.000Z","msg":"On9都做到CIA?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n做間諜通常下場都好慘。尤其做中共間諜，佢點可能相信一個曾經背叛自己國家嘅人？<br />\n<br />\n你幫佢做完野，你就只會成為Condom。<br />\n<br />\n留明睇中共發言話冇咁嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n完全唔識呢條友。"},{"pid":"b033c51adef1e474330a807611c5ad33e3830a46","tid":1134691,"uid":37586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T02:10:37.000Z","msg":"長洲原居民移民左美國都要幫支那做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要有過億身家會為左幾十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/152518/01%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6-%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%A2cia-%E9%9B%99%E9%9D%A2%E8%AB%9C%E7%82%BA%E9%95%B7%E6%B4%B2%E5%8E%9F%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91-%E5%B1%85%E6%B8%AF%E7%88%B6%E6%AF%8D%E5%85%84%E9%95%B7%E7%8F%BE%E8%BA%AB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F152518%2F01%25E7%258D%25A8%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2594%25A2cia-%25E9%259B%2599%25E9%259D%25A2%25E8%25AB%259C%25E7%2582%25BA%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E5%258E%259F%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2588%25B6%25E6%25AF%258D%25E5%2585%2584%25E9%2595%25B7%25E7%258F%25BE%25E8%25BA%25AB&d=P2v3VPQ3iBAPr6cjv61qmRPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=091db92a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/152518/01%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6-%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%A2cia-%E9%9B%99%E9%9D%A2%E8%AB%9C%E7%82%BA%E9%95%B7%E6%B4%B2%E5%8E%9F%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91-%E5%B1%85%E6%B8%AF%E7%88%B6%E6%AF%8D%E5%85%84%E9%95%B7%E7%8F%BE%E8%BA%AB</a>"},{"pid":"48eb98a2e3c2a86163858bb2f9a8b296c0d77448","tid":1134691,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b033c51adef1e474330a807611c5ad33e3830a46","tid":1134691,"uid":37586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T02:10:37.000Z","msg":"長洲原居民移民左美國都要幫支那做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要有過億身家會為左幾十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%